message: Finally, you can get 10x optical zoom on a smartphone using the Hasselblad True Zoom Mod and Moto Z. Now that is different.
Not a minor improvement. Not a little design tweak. We’ve reimagined what a smartphone can be. Get the Moto Z with Moto Mods and say Hello Moto.
